0 This screen shows your hero's income and expenses. Most of the numbers will change continuously as they are re-calculated each "game day". A "game day" is unique to every player and depends on how much action the player takes. The game day of an active player that walks, fights and discovers new lands, approximately equals 5 minutes of real time. When a player is inactive, the game time freezes. The army stops consuming gold, but the hero does not earn any income either. The amount of the hero's personal income depends on his Trade skill. If you want to have a greater income, upgrade this skill.
